Span.Text: Microsoft solutions allow new innovations to be delivered at scale and in concert, transforming the way Government workers deliver services to citizens and colleagues.

Streamline case management and deliver world-class enterprise case resolution by customising and automating rules, event triggers and work flows based on entitlements and SLA’s. Define and customise organisation-wide KPI’s, while creating quick response and swarming teams by integrated SLA triggers through collaboration tools such as Yammer, email, and workflow notification.

Increase productivity through shared services across multiple organizations and provide instant, role-tailored access to data to help users prioritize tasks and connect key business processes with results.

Collect, organise, and use community data to improve data quality and drive innovation.  Employ crowd-sourced problem solving and real-time citizen collaboration to fully utilise community expertise. Leverage smart infrastructure, consumer device data, and citizen feedback as data inputs to systems.

Improve collaboration with rich presence information that helps employees find each other and choose the most effective way to communicate. Instead of sending email documents back and forth for approval, workers can rely on real-time collaboration through virtual whiteboard sharing.
